    • nested

      public static <T extends org.openqa.selenium.SearchContext> Criteria<T> nested(MultipleSearchSupplier<?> howToFind)
      The checking of an element/widget by presence of nested elements.
      Type Parameters:
      T - is a type of element/widget
      Parameters:
      howToFind - is the way to find nested elements.

      NOTE!!!

      When there is a timeout passed through MultipleSearchSupplier.timeOut(Duration) of the given howToFind then it is ignored here.
      Returns:
      criteria that checks/filters an element/widget

    • nested

      public static <T extends org.openqa.selenium.SearchContext> Criteria<T> nested(MultipleSearchSupplier<?> howToFind, int expected)
      The checking of an element/widget by presence of nested elements
      Type Parameters:
      T - is a type of element/widget
      Parameters:
      howToFind - is the way to find nested elements.

      NOTE!!!

      When there is a timeout passed through MultipleSearchSupplier.timeOut(Duration) of the given howToFind then it is ignored here.
      expected - is the count of expected nested elements
      Returns:
      criteria that checks/filters an element/widget
